      "title": "Protestors march to Sri Lanka prime minister\u2019s office facing police tear gas",
      "author": "Chanka Jayasinghe",
      "body_lines": [
        "ECONOMYNEXT \u2013 Sri Lanka police fired teargas at protestors marching to the Prime Minister\u2019s office located on Flower Road, Colombo, after reports emerged that President Gotabaya Rajapaksa fled the country leading to speculation that Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe will be sworn in as Acting President.",
        "The protestors have managed to break through a police barricade near the PM\u2019s office, despite tear gas and water canon fire.",
        "The protestors are now heading towards the PM\u2019s office. (Colombo/Jul13/2022)"
      ],
